graphic.name: AMD Radeon RX 6600 XT
graphic.description: GIGABYTE AMD Radeon RX 6600 XT GAMING OC PRO 8G graphics card delivers ultra-high frame rates and serious 4K gameplay. Get the ultimate gaming experience with powerful new compute units, amazing AMD Infinity Cache, and up to 8GB of dedicated GDDR6 memory. And, when paired with an AMD Ryzen Series desktop processor, AMD Smart Access Memory technology offers new levels of gaming performance.
